      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIKE DYNAMITE (3) was never in contention last time at Bendigo, but prior to that won by 0.8 lengths at Healesville (19.79) beating Wilkie Twycross in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 on June 16. Worth another chance. PAW LASSIE (1) doesn't win out of turn. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when third (24.40) at Bendigo. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Hard to beat again. DREAM BIG (2) scored two back in one of the fastest times on the card then was always well back and could manage only a 10 length 7th at this track (23.28) latest. Should be thereabouts. TINKER DOT (4) is a last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
